{"id":70,"parent_id":64,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":70,"title":"Jacob 6","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jacob","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 6"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord will recover Israel in the last days—The world will be burned with fire—Men must follow Christ to avoid the lake of fire and brimstone. About 544–421",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.1","order":"05.14.006.7744"},["b","1"],"And now, behold, my brethren, as I said unto you that I would prophesy, behold, this is my prophecy—that the things which this prophet",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Zenos"],"spake, concerning the house of Israel, in the which he likened them unto a tame",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"olive tree"],", must surely come to pass."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.2","order":"05.14.006.7745"},["b","2"],"And the day that he shall set his hand again the second time to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"recover"],"his people, is the day, yea, even the last time, that the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"servants"],"of the Lord shall go forth in his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"power"],", to",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"nourish"],"and prune his",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_2e"},"vineyard"],"; and after that the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_2f"},"end"],"soon cometh."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.3","order":"05.14.006.7746"},["b","3"],"And how",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"blessed"],"are they who have labored",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"diligently"],"in his vineyard; and how",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"cursed"],"are they who shall be cast out into their own place! And the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"world"],"shall be",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_3e"},"burned"],"with fire."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.4","order":"05.14.006.7747"},["b","4"],"And how merciful is our God unto us, for he remembereth the house of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Israel"],", both roots and branches; and he stretches forth his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"hands"],"unto them all the day long; and they are a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"stiffnecked"],"and a gainsaying people; but as many as will not harden their hearts shall be saved in the kingdom of God."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.5","order":"05.14.006.7748"},["b","5"],"Wherefore, my beloved brethren, I beseech of you in words of soberness that ye would repent, and come with full purpose of heart, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"cleave"],"unto God as he cleaveth unto you. And while his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"arm"],"of mercy is extended towards you in the light of the day, harden not your hearts."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.6","order":"05.14.006.7749"},["b","6"],"Yea, today, if ye will hear his voice, harden not your hearts; for why will ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"die"],"?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.7","order":"05.14.006.7750"},["b","7"],"For behold, after ye have been nourished by the good",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"word"],"of God all the day long, will ye bring forth evil fruit, that ye must be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"hewn"],"down and cast into the fire?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.8","order":"05.14.006.7751"},["b","8"],"Behold, will ye reject these words? Will ye reject the words of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"prophets"],"; and will ye reject all the words which have been spoken concerning Christ, after so many have spoken concerning him; and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"deny"],"the good word of Christ, and the power of God, and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"gift"],"of the Holy Ghost, and quench the Holy Spirit, and make a",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"mock"],"of the great plan of redemption, which hath been laid for you?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.9","order":"05.14.006.7752"},["b","9"],"Know ye not that if ye will do these things, that the power of the redemption and the resurrection, which is in Christ, will bring you to stand with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"shame"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"awful"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"guilt"],"before the bar of God?"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.10","order":"05.14.006.7753"},["b","10"],"And according to the power of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"justice"],", for justice cannot be denied, ye must go away into that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"lake"],"of fire and brimstone, whose flames are unquenchable, and whose smoke ascendeth up forever and ever, which lake of fire and brimstone is",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"endless"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"torment"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.11","order":"05.14.006.7754"},["b","11"],"O then, my beloved brethren, repent ye, and enter in at the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"strait gate"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"continue"],"in the way which is narrow, until ye shall obtain eternal life."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.12","order":"05.14.006.7755"},["b","12"],"O be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"wise"],"; what can I say more?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.13","order":"05.14.006.7756"},["b","13"],"Finally, I bid you farewell, until I shall meet you before the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"pleasing"],"bar of God, which bar striketh the wicked with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"awful"],"dread and fear. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.1a","order":"05.14.006.7757"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.1"},"Jacob 5:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/33.13.13-15"},"Alma 33:13 (13–15)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-lost"},"TG Scriptures, Lost"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.1b","order":"05.14.006.7759"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/11.21.1-36"},"Rom. 11:21 (1–36)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/10.12"},"1 Ne. 10:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.3.3-77"},"Jacob 5:3 (3–77)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.2a","order":"05.14.006.7761"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.12.10-12"},"1 Ne. 22:12 (10–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.11"},"D&C 110:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/137.6"},"137:6"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-gathering-of"},"TG Israel, Gathering of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-restoration-of"},"Israel, Restoration of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.2b","order":"05.14.006.7763"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.61"},"Jacob 5:61"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.2c","order":"05.14.006.7765"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.1,14"},"1 Ne. 14:1, 14"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.2d","order":"05.14.006.7767"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.71"},"Jacob 5:71"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.56"},"D&C 101:56"],"."],["div",{"id":"2e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.2e","order":"05.14.006.7769"},["b","2e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/12.10"},"Jer. 12:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.56"},"D&C 138:56"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vineyard-of-the-lord"},"TG Vineyard of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"2f","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.2f","order":"05.14.006.7771"},["b","2f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/30.10"},"2 Ne. 30:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.29"},"Jacob 5:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.17.17-20,28"},"D&C 43:17 (17–20, 28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.3a","order":"05.14.006.7773"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.71"},"Jacob 5:71"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.3b","order":"05.14.006.7775"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/diligence"},"TG Diligence"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/perseverance"},"Perseverance"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.3c","order":"05.14.006.7777"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/41.1"},"D&C 41:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.3d","order":"05.14.006.7779"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world"},"TG World"],"."],["div",{"id":"3e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.3e","order":"05.14.006.7781"},["b","3e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.6"},"Isa. 24:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/27.2"},"2 Ne. 27:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.77"},"Jacob 5:77"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/25.1"},"3 Ne. 25:1"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world-end-of"},"TG World, End of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.4a","order":"05.14.006.7783"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.24"},"2 Sam. 7:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.4b","order":"05.14.006.7785"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/9.19.18-26"},"Neh. 9:19 (18–26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.17.17-21"},"2 Ne. 19:17 (17–21)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.32"},"28:32"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.47"},"Jacob 5:47"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.4c","order":"05.14.006.7787"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stiffnecked"},"TG Stiffnecked"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.5a","order":"05.14.006.7789"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/10.20"},"Deut. 10:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.8"},"Josh. 23:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/18.6"},"2 Kgs. 18:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/4.25"},"Hel. 4:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/11.19"},"D&C 11:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.5b","order":"05.14.006.7791"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/59.16"},"Isa. 59:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/1.15"},"2 Ne. 1:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.33"},"Alma 5:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/9.14"},"3 Ne. 9:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.6a","order":"05.14.006.7793"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.28.26-28,32"},"Ezek. 18:28 (26–28, 32)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.7a","order":"05.14.006.7795"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/119.28"},"Ps. 119:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.7b","order":"05.14.006.7797"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.52"},"Alma 5:52"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.11.11-12"},"3 Ne. 27:11 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.8a","order":"05.14.006.7799"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/26.5"},"Jer. 26:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.8b","order":"05.14.006.7801"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-loss-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Loss of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.8c","order":"05.14.006.7803"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gift-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gift of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.8d","order":"05.14.006.7805"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrilege"},"TG Sacrilege"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.9a","order":"05.14.006.7807"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.9b","order":"05.14.006.7809"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/7.19"},"Jacob 7:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.26"},"Mosiah 15:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.9c","order":"05.14.006.7811"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/guilt"},"TG Guilt"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment-the-last"},"Judgment, the Last"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.10a","order":"05.14.006.7813"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-justice-of"},"TG God, Justice of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justice"},"Justice"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.10b","order":"05.14.006.7815"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.20"},"Rev. 19:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.23"},"2 Ne. 28:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.27"},"Mosiah 3:27"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hell"},"TG Hell"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.10c","order":"05.14.006.7817"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/2.33"},"Mosiah 2:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.11.10-12"},"D&C 19:11 (10–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.10d","order":"05.14.006.7819"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/damnation"},"TG Damnation"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.11a","order":"05.14.006.7821"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.41"},"2 Ne. 9:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.11b","order":"05.14.006.7823"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.15"},"2 Ne. 31:15"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/commitment"},"TG Commitment"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.12a","order":"05.14.006.7825"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.16"},"Matt. 10:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/9.28"},"Morm. 9:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.13a","order":"05.14.006.7827"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.34"},"Moro. 10:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/6.13b","order":"05.14.006.7829"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/40.14"},"Alma 40:14"],"."]]}
